Package rescuecore2.misc.geometry.spatialindex

Interface Summary
Indexable Interface for things that can go into a spatial index.
Region An indexable region.
SpatialIndex Top-level interface for spatial index implementations.
 

Class Summary
AbstractSpatialIndex Abstract base class for spatial index implementations.
BBTree A spatial index that creates a (probably) unbalanced tree of bounding boxes.
LineRegion A line region.
NullRegion An empty region.
PointRegion A point region.
RectangleRegion A rectangular region.
Tools Useful tools for R* tree building.
